<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ض ج ج:</span> <span class="c2">(أَضَجَّ)</span> الْقَوْمُ <span class="c2">(إِضْجَاجًا)</span> جَلَبُوا وَصَاحُوا.<span class="c5"> فَإِنْ جَزِعُوا مِنْ شَيْءٍ وَغَلَبُوا قِيلَ:</span> <span class="c2">(ضَجُّوا)</span> يَضِجُّونَ بِالْكَسْرِ <span class="c2">(ضَجِيجًا)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(الضَّجَّةُ)</span> الْجَلَبَةُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>